{
  "texts": [
    "Adaptive Exponential (AdEx) LIF.",
    "Adaptive exponential LIF model involves two state parameters, membrane potential, u(t) and adaptation variables w k to explain various spiking dynamics 12, 34.",
    "The evolution of u(t) and w k are described by the following equations:",
    "where Δ T is the sharpness parameter, v th threshold potential, w k adaptation current, a k adaptation parameter, b k amount by which adaptation current increases after threshold.",
    "Spike response model."
